annotationA: Ribosomal protein L22-like is a eukaryotic-specific component of the large ribosomal subunit involved in protein synthesis
annotationB: 60S ribosomal protein L27a; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL15 family
